headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
There are many ways to take to the skies this week in GTA Online – if you need help getting airborne, there are deals on planes, helicopters and Hangars, as well as a selection of high-powered cars.

- RO-86 Alkonost – 25% off
- Buckingham Valkyrie – 40% off
- Coil Cyclone – 40% off
- Hangars – 30% off

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
